Sales and Profit Analysis Dashboard

This dashboard provides a 360Â° view of sales, profit, and order distribution across categories, segments, and regions. It showcases:

- Orders by segment and category to track performance distribution.

- Category-wise and subcategory-wise sales & AOV for product-level insights.

- Profit trends by day and country to highlight high and low performing regions.

- Day-wise sales patterns to identify demand fluctuations over time.

It helps businesses monitor key metrics, optimize product strategies, and improve decision-making for revenue growth.
